Sunday push 🔥 few reasons why i love lifting:

1. Mental and physical wellness 🧠, Earth can get ghetto. 

2. One of my sisters suffered from addiction and passed unexpectedly in 2021. A lot of times under a heavy weight, she comes to mind. She missed out on a lot in life, so I push 2x 🦋 

3. & Nothing like a lil friendly competition 🔥Women’s Figure Bodybuilding

Tafari Campbell, my client, and the Obama’s personal Chef. Words can’t even express the shock and sadness. You were one of my best client I ever had and one of my favorites. I’m sending my sincerest condolences to the Campbell family and the Obama family for their loss. Here’s a few clips of what I was able to capture of Tafari. 

You know, Tafari was confidential about his career and every time he said he’s headed to Martha’s Vineyard or Hawaii, I had an intuition.. and I would say “ who you cookin for?!? you must be with the Obamas or somethin..”. Today confirmed. Heartbroken and never forgotten Tafari. cheftafari @thymeless_creations 🙏🏽
